data.description: Check out this Well Loved 3 Bedroom 2 Bathroom 2 car garage home! Conveniently located just minutes off of Spring hill drive close to The Veteran's expressway and the Anderson snow sports complex! A few upgrades this home has to offer is a lovely PVC privacy fenced backyard, gardening shed, Screened in back porch, Newer Roof, Newer Trane A/C system, ADT security, Granite counters in the kitchen and Lovely Laminate wood floors throughout the kitchen, dining and living room! A split floor plan with a 13x16 Primary bedroom! This property makes for a perfect starter home, retirement or investment property. Schedule your private tour today!
